explanation.summary: Kt qu in tim cho thy nhp tim ca bn p chm hn bnh thng (Nhp chm), nhng cc tn hiu in khc ca tim vn u n.
explanation.details: Hnh nh sng in tim cho thy cc nhp p ca tim din ra u n nhng cc khong cch gia chng xa hn bnh thng. C th, nhp tim ca bn l 54.38 ln/pht, thp hn mc chun thng thng (60-100 ln/pht). iu ny c ngha l tim ang bm mu vi tc  chm hn mt cht. Tuy nhin, thi gian dn truyn in tim (QRS 0.11s) vn trong gii hn an ton, cho thy cc bung tim co bp ng b, khng c du hiu tc nghn ng dn truyn in.
explanation.recommendations: Nu bn khng cm thy chng mt, mt mi hay kh th, tnh trng nhp chm ny c th khng ng ngi, c bit nu bn l ngi thng xuyn tp th dc hoc ang dng mt s loi thuc. Bn nn theo di cc triu chng ca mnh.
explanation.next_steps: Bn nn trao i vi bc s  xem xt liu nhp tim chm ny c phi l bnh thng i vi c th bn hay do nguyn nhn no khc. Nu xut hin cc triu chng nh ngt xu, chng mt, mt mi hoc kh th, hy n c s y t ngay lp tc.
